<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Zap Anônimo - Em Manutenção</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .maintenance-container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 24px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .icon-container {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .gear-icon {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
        }

        .gear {
            fill: #25D366;
            animation: rotate 4s linear infinite;
            transform-origin: center;
        }

        .gear-small {
            fill: #128C7E;
            animation: rotate-reverse 3s linear infinite;
            transform-origin: center;
        }

        @keyframes rotate {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        @keyframes rotate-reverse {
            from { transform: rotate(360deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(0deg); }
        }

        .whatsapp-badge {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: #25D366;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.3);
        }

        .whatsapp-badge svg {
            width: 35px;
            height: 35px;
            fill: white;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #25D366;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 3px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            width: 60%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #25D366, #128C7E);
            border-radius: 3px;
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.6; }
        }

        .status-text {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.1);
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            color: #25D366;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .status-dot {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            background: #25D366;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: blink 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.3; }
        }

        .footer-text {
            margin-top: 40px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .maintenance-container {
                padding: 40px 25px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 26px;
            }

            .subtitle {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="maintenance-container">
        <div class="whatsapp-badge">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <h1>Estamos em Manutenção</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Voltamos em breve!</p>

        <p>
            Nosso sistema está passando por melhorias para oferecer
            uma experiência ainda melhor para você. Agradecemos sua
            paciência e compreensão.
        </p>

        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-fill"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="status-text">
            <span class="status-dot"></span>
            Manutenção em andamento
        </div>

        <p class="footer-text">
            Zap Anônimo &copy; 2025 - Todos os direitos reservados
        </p>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Bloqueia navegação e acesso
        history.pushState(null, null, location.href);
        window.onpopstate = function () {
            history.go(1);
        };

        // Bloqueia atalhos de teclado
        document.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
            if (e.ctrlKey || e.metaKey) {
                e.preventDefault();
            }
        });

        // Remove qualquer localStorage/sessionStorage
        localStorage.clear();
        sessionStorage.clear();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
